Built-in material allowing the user to test the package with demo data

Source: R/01-utils.R
madshapR_DEMO.Rd

Built-in tibbles and lists allowing the user to test the package with demo material.

madshapR_DEMO

Format

list

A list with 20 elements used for testing the package (data frames and lists):

data_dict_MELBOURNE

Data dictionary of Melbourne dataset

data_dict_PARIS

Data dictionary of Paris dataset

data_dict_PARIS - flatten

Data dictionary of Paris in preprocessed format

data_dict_TOKYO

Data dictionary of Tokyo dataset

data_dict_TOKYO - with errors

Tagged data dictionary of Tokyo dataset containing errors for testing purpose

data_dictt_TOKYO - with errors in data

data dictionary of Tokyo dataset containing errors with for testing purpose

dataset_MELBOURNE

Dataset of Melbourne

dataset_PARIS

Dataset of Paris

dataset_TOKYO

Dataset of Tokyo

data_dict_TOKYO - with errors in data

Dataset of Tokyo containing errors for testing purpose

...

Examples

{

 print(madshapR_DEMO$dataset_TOKYO)

}
